{"word":"ἐπαυλίζομαι","slug":"ἐπαυλίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαυλίζομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> with <a href='S:aorist tense'>aor.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a>, <i>to encamp on the field</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to encamp near</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}